A 28-year-old man, Abdullahi Adamu, has allegedly raped a five-year-old nursery 3 schoolgirl (name withheld) in Adamawa State.SaharaReporters learnt that the alleged randy pedophile, lured the minor into an uncompleted building in Mubi in the Mubi North Local Government Area of the State, where he manhandled and had carnal knowledge of her. Illustration



The five-year-old minor attends Halibath Nursery/Primary school, at Anguwan Madina, near Adamu’s residence in Mubi town.This came amidst the unsettled dust of the gruesome murder of another kindergarten girl, Hanifa Abubakar, weeks after she was abducted in Kano State.Adamu, who allegedly took time to pry on the little kid, took advantage of her on the fateful day while returning home from school alone. He reportedly lured her into the hideout with a N20 biscuit where he raped her.“I asked her to come with me to a nearby shop to pick a biscuit and she obliged me, after which I took her into the uncompleted building,” Adamu said.A curious neighbour, who sighted him while exiting the building with such a minor, suspected and alerted other neighbors, leading to his arrest.Examinations at the General Hospital Mubi, established that Adamu had penetrated the kid.As things stood, he had been arraigned at the Chief Magistrate Court II, before Magistrate Hamidu Aminu. Meantime, the judge ordered that the defendant be remanded in prison custody.